    public class AircraftMGRSLatitudeBandAndGridSquare
extends AbstractMGRSLatitudeBandAndGridSquare
    MGRS Latitude Band and Grid Square (ST0806 Tag 15).

    Third, fourth and fifth characters of Aircraft MGRS coordinates. Third character is the alpha code for the latitude band (A through Z, omitting I and O). Fourth and fifth characters are the 2-character alpha code for the grid square designator (WGS 84). Note that latitude bands A & B correspond to Antarctic UPS regions and Y & Z correspond to Arctic UPS regions.
